oboard2-3b6dd9c6b3c559ed3c3ce402aaff7420-85e3d.jpg 885w,\n/static/protoboard2-3b6dd9c6b3c559ed3c3ce402aaff7420-d1924.jpg 1180w,\n/static/protoboard2-3b6dd9c6b3c559ed3c3ce402aaff7420-c1266.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-c1266.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 65.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"protoboard3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-f8fb9.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-e8976.jpg 148w,\n/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-63df2.jpg 295w,\n/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-f8fb9.jpg 590w,\n/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-85e3d.jpg 885w,\n/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-d1924.jpg 1180w,\n/static/protoboard3-2dce725c029c6878b2e3af2b4469a685-c1266.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>","frontmatter":{"title":"üõ†Ô∏è Hardware","date":"May 03, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/hardware/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/frontend/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"üñº